---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Dear User — Your AI Collaboration partner" active="home">

<style>
  /* Hero ----------------------------------------------------------- */
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 88px 24px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-action-600);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 76px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 820px;
  }
  .hero h1 .accent { color: var(--c-action-600); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.7vw, 19px);
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 28px 0 36px;
  }
  .hero-sub p { margin: 0 0 12px; }
  .hero-sub p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .hero-example-link {
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .hero-example-link:hover {
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    border-color: var(--c-ink-500);
  }
  .hero-restart-hint {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  /* Install block --------------------------------------------------- */
  .install {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--c-paper-100);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .install:hover { border-color: var(--c-accent-500); background: var(--c-paper-50); }
  .install .prompt { color: var(--c-ink-400); }
  .install .cmd { color: var(--c-ink-900); }
  .install .copy {
    margin-left: 6px;
    font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--c-paper-200);
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  .install:hover .copy { background: var(--c-action-100); color: var(--c-action-700); }

  /* Quick-facts row under hero -------------------------------------- */
  .hero-facts {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 22px 32px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
  }
  .hero-facts .dot {
    color: var(--c-action-600);
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  /* Features grid --------------------------------------------------- */
  .features-section {
    padding: 72px 0 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
  }
  .section-head {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-400);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .section-sub {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
  }
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .feature {
    background: var(--c-paper-100);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .feature:hover {
    border-color: var(--c-accent-500);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .feature-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 9px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    background: var(--c-action-100);
    color: var(--c-action-700);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .feature h3 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
  }
  .feature p {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
  }
  .feature ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .feature ul li {
    padding-left: 18px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .feature ul li:before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--c-action-600);
  }
  .feature-cmd {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    background: var(--c-paper-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    padding: 7px 11px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-top: auto;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .feature-cmd .fn { color: var(--c-ink-900); }

  /* "Also included" row (onboard/wrapped/history) ------------------- */
  .also {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 48px auto 0;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }
  .also-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-400);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .also-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .also-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .also-item {
    background: var(--c-paper-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
  }
  .also-item h4 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 17px;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
  }
  .also-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
  }

  /* Share section --------------------------------------------------- */
  .share {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
  }
  .share-inner {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .share-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
  }
  .share-copy h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }
  .share-copy p {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .share-copy .share-url {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    background: var(--c-paper-100);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
  }
  .share-copy .share-url .path { color: var(--c-action-600); }
  .share-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
    margin-top: 16px !important;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* Share card mock ------------------------------------------------- */
  .share-card-mock {
    aspect-ratio: 1200 / 630;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-paper-100) 0%, var(--c-paper-50) 100%);
    padding: 36px 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -20px rgba(31, 26, 20, 0.15);
  }
  .share-card-mock .sc-mark {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
  }
  .share-card-mock .sc-mark svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
  .share-card-mock .sc-body {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .share-card-mock .sc-score {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 11vw, 96px);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--c-action-600);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .share-card-mock .sc-score-unit {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--c-ink-400);
  }
  .share-card-mock .sc-label {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.8vw, 20px);
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    max-width: 60%;
  }
  .share-card-mock .sc-foot {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-400);
  }

  /* Report excerpt (replaces share-card-mock content) -------------- */
  .report-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-family: 'Geist', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--c-action-600);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .report-cta:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  .report-excerpt {
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--c-paper-50);
    padding: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -20px rgba(31, 26, 20, 0.15);
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-date {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-400);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-greeting {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 36px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    margin: 0 0 22px;
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-scores {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-score {
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px;
    background: var(--c-paper-100);
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-score-label {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-dot.good { background: var(--c-good); }
  .report-excerpt .re-dot.warn { background: var(--c-warn); }
  .report-excerpt .re-dot.bad { background: var(--c-bad); }
  .report-excerpt .re-score-num {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .report-excerpt .re-score-num.good { color: var(--c-good); }
  .report-excerpt .re-score-num.warn { color: var(--c-warn); }
  .report-excerpt .re-score-num.bad { color: var(--c-bad); }
  .report-excerpt .re-lede {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Social proof placeholder --------------------------------------- */
  .social-proof {
    padding: 56px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .social-proof .sp-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-400);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .social-proof .sp-placeholder {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--c-paper-300);
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: var(--c-ink-500);
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* How it works ---------------------------------------------------- */
  .how {
    padding: 72px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
  }
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 28px;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .step {
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--c-paper-100);
  }
  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--c-action-600);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .step h4 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
  }
  .step p {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .step code {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    background: var(--c-paper-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  /* Honest FAQ ------------------------------------------------------ */
  .faq {
    padding: 72px 0 88px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
  }
  .faq-list {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    padding: 22px 0;
  }
  .faq-item:first-of-type { border-top: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200); }
  .faq-item[open] summary .faq-mark { transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .faq-item summary {
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary:hover { color: var(--c-action-600); }
  .faq-mark {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--c-action-600);
    line-height: 1.35;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .faq-answer {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--c-ink-700);
    margin: 14px 0 0;
    padding-right: 36px;
  }
  .faq-answer code {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: var(--c-paper-100);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
  }

  /* Pull quote ------------------------------------------------------ */
  .pullquote {
    padding: 72px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-paper-200);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pullquote blockquote {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 36px);
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--c-ink-900);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--c-action-600);
  }
  .pullquote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-ink-400);
  }
</style>

<!-- Hero ------------------------------------------------------------- -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">
    
    Your AI collaboration partner
  </div>
  <h1>
    
    Dear User,<br/>how's the collaboration with your <span class="accent">agent?</span>
  </h1>

  <div class="hero-sub">
    <p>
      
      This year, you'll spend more hours with your AI agent than with most people in your life. Dear User was built to make the most of those hours.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-actions">
    <div class="install" id="install-cta" data-analytics="install-copy" title="Click to copy">
      <span class="prompt">$</span>
      <span class="cmd">claude mcp add --scope user dearuser -- npx -y @poisedhq/dearuser-mcp@latest</span>
      <span class="copy" id="copy-label">
        Copy
      </span>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-restart-hint">
      
      Restart Claude Code afterwards so the tools appear.
    </p>
    <a href="/example" class="hero-example-link">
      
      Or see an example →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
  var cta = document.getElementById('install-cta');
  var label = document.getElementById('copy-label');
  var cmd = 'claude mcp add --scope user dearuser -- npx -y @poisedhq/dearuser-mcp@latest';
  if (cta) {
    cta.addEventListener('click', function () {
      if (!navigator.clipboard) return;
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(cmd).then(function () {
        if (!label) return;
        var html = label.innerHTML;
        label.innerHTML = 'Copied';
        setTimeout(function () { label.innerHTML = html; }, 1600);
      }).catch(function () {});
    });
  }
</script>

<!-- Features --------------------------------------------------------- -->
<section class="features-section" id="features">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">
      What you get
    </div>
    <h2 class="section-title">
      
      Dear User helps humans and AI agents understand each other better.
    </h2>
    <p class="section-sub">
      
      We read your setup like a new colleague who actually pays attention — then write back about where you're repeating yourself, where keys are leaking, and where your setup is quietly drifting apart.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="features-grid">
    <!-- Collab -->
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="feature-badge">
        Collab
      </span>
      <h3>
        
        How you two work together.
      </h3>
      <p>
        
        A score for your collaboration, your agent's "archetype", and concrete suggestions — not just "consider better instructions".
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Catches patterns: corrections you make over and over</li>
        <li>Suggestions with code snippets ready to paste</li>
        <li>Tells you where your setup is strong</li>
      </ul>
      <span class="feature-cmd"><span class="fn">mcp__dearuser__collab</span></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Security — emphasize secrets -->
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="feature-badge">
        Security
      </span>
      <h3>
        
        Looks for keys you forgot.
      </h3>
      <p>
        
        Scans your Claude files for leaked API keys (OpenAI, Anthropic, GitHub, AWS, Stripe and 8 other types) and pulls signals from the platforms you already use.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>12 secret types caught in instructions, memory, hooks and skills</li>
        <li>Pulls warnings from GitHub, Supabase, npm and Vercel — when you've set up tokens</li>
        <li>Catches rules that contradict each other (e.g. "never force-push" + a hook that does)</li>
      </ul>
      <span class="feature-cmd"><span class="fn">mcp__dearuser__security</span></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Health -->
    <div class="feature">
      <span class="feature-badge">
        Health
      </span>
      <h3>
        
        What's quietly broken?
      </h3>
      <p>
        
